description: Praetorian Property, Inc. engages in acquiring, rehabilitating, and selling or leasing distressed properties in the United States. Its property portfolio comprises single family, multi-family, and commercial properties. The company was formerly known as Cannabis-Rx Inc. and changed its name to Praetorian Property, Inc. in September 2015. Praetorian Property, Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Scottsdale, Arizona. Praetorian Property, Inc. is a subsidiary of Miramar Investors Inc.
